[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 1.0,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.0,
    "endTime": 1.0,
    "text": "Please!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.0,
    "endTime": 2.0,
    "text": "I said I'd come back!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.0,
    "endTime": 3.0,
    "text": "I'm not doing anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.0,
    "endTime": 6.0,
    "text": "Oh, that's your normal face, isn't it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.0,
    "endTime": 7.0,
    "text": "Hmm..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.0,
    "endTime": 11.0,
    "text": "The only problem is, you need to pass a test in order to prove you belong in my class."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.0,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "So, you're gonna have to study like you've never studied before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.0,
    "endTime": 16.0,
    "text": "Let's go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.0,
    "endTime": 18.0,
    "text": "You gotta think big."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.0,
    "endTime": 19.0,
    "text": "Think deep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 23.0,
    "text": "Pretty soon, you'll make that quantum leap."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.0,
    "endTime": 26.0,
    "text": "So?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.0,
    "endTime": 27.0,
    "text": "What do I do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.0,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "I've literally never studied before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "Are you kidding me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 31.0,
    "text": "All these years of teaching you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.0,
    "endTime": 35.0,
    "text": "Just go to your mind palace or whatever and try to remember how to study!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.0,
    "endTime": 36.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 38.0,
    "text": "I'll try."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.0,
    "endTime": 45.0,
    "text": "More like a mind cupboard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 47.0,
    "text": "Okay, Watterson."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.0,
    "endTime": 48.0,
    "text": "Time to roll up your sleeves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.0,
    "endTime": 49.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.0,
    "endTime": 50.0,
    "text": "More work?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.0,
    "endTime": 50.0,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.0,
    "endTime": 53.0,
    "text": "Roll up your sleeves so I can write the answers on your arm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.0,
    "endTime": 53.0,
    "text": "But that's cheating!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 59.0,
    "text": "Yeah, but if you rearrange the letters in the word teaching, what do you get?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.0,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "Uh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 61.0,
    "text": "Eating?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.0,
    "endTime": 62.0,
    "text": "Cha?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.0,
    "endTime": 62.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.0,
    "endTime": 63.0,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.0,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "Cheating!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.0,
    "endTime": 65.0,
    "text": "But isn't that wrong?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.0,
    "endTime": 67.0,
    "text": "Only if you get caught."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.0,
    "endTime": 69.0,
    "text": "Look, when I was your age, I cheated too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.0,
    "endTime": 71.0,
    "text": "What the what right now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.0,
    "endTime": 73.0,
    "text": "I scribbled the answers on the cave wall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.0,
    "endTime": 76.0,
    "text": "Oh, so that's what cave paintings are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.0,
    "endTime": 78.0,
    "text": "Okay, what's the best way for me to cheat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.0,
    "endTime": 80.0,
    "text": "In your case, every way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.0,
    "endTime": 82.0,
    "text": "Right, Watterson."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.0,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "You have one hour."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 86.0,
    "text": "Begin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.0,
    "endTime": 90.0,
    "text": "Okay, plan A."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.0,
    "endTime": 96.0,
    "text": "I can't read it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.0,
    "endTime": 97.0,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.0,
    "endTime": 98.0,
    "text": "It's all backwards."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.0,
    "endTime": 99.0,
    "text": "I wrote it in front of a mirror."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.0,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "Okay, plan B."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 103.0,
    "text": "Oh, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.0,
    "endTime": 105.0,
    "text": "It goes dark when I close my eyes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 107.0,
    "text": "Just pull on them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 109.0,
    "text": "Watch out!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.0,
    "endTime": 112.0,
    "text": "What is going on here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.0,
    "endTime": 116.0,
    "text": "Just, uh, visualizing my answers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.0,
    "endTime": 119.0,
    "text": "Oh, I've always wondered what that would look like from the outside."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "Carry on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "Plan C, then."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.0,
    "endTime": 123.0,
    "text": "Sir?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.0,
    "endTime": 124.0,
    "text": "Yes?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.0,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "Can I use the bathroom?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 126.0,
    "text": "Hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.0,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "So, did you use the notes we left in there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.0,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "Yep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.0,
    "endTime": 136.0,
    "text": "Ah, good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.0,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "I have to say, I prefer to apply paper."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.0,
    "endTime": 139.0,
    "text": "It's softer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.0,
    "endTime": 140.0,
    "text": "What the?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.0,
    "endTime": 142.0,
    "text": "Okay, next plan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.0,
    "endTime": 143.0,
    "text": "Use the water bottle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.0,
    "endTime": 144.0,
    "text": "Oh, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.0,
    "endTime": 144.0,
    "text": "Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 146.0,
    "text": "I meant the label."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.0,
    "endTime": 147.0,
    "text": "Read the label!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.0,
    "endTime": 149.0,
    "text": "Recycle after use."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.0,
    "endTime": 150.0,
    "text": "Oh, of course."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.0,
    "endTime": 154.0,
    "text": "The answers were written inside the label!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 155.0,
    "text": "What is wrong with you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.0,
    "endTime": 157.0,
    "text": "Use these!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.0,
    "endTime": 158.0,
    "text": "I can't read that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.0,
    "endTime": 159.0,
    "text": "Don't worry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.0,
    "endTime": 160.0,
    "text": "I've got this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.0,
    "endTime": 162.0,
    "text": "Never mind."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.0,
    "endTime": 163.0,
    "text": "I'll write the answers on the window."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.0,
    "endTime": 166.0,
    "text": "Ah, ah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.0,
    "endTime": 168.0,
    "text": "Dag nabbit, it's too hot outside."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.0,
    "endTime": 171.0,
    "text": "Ahhhhhhh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.0,
    "endTime": 174.0,
    "text": "Watson, you have five minutes remaining."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.0,
    "endTime": 175.0,
    "text": "I'll just whime it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.0,
    "endTime": 177.0,
    "text": "First answer, the birth of Venus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.0,
    "endTime": 178.0,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.0,
    "endTime": 179.0,
    "text": "That's not really necessary!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.0,
    "endTime": 180.0,
    "text": "I can hear you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.0,
    "endTime": 181.0,
    "text": "Good point."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.0,
    "endTime": 182.0,
    "text": "Question two."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.0,
    "endTime": 183.0,
    "text": "Tom, we don't have time for this!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.0,
    "endTime": 184.0,
    "text": "I'm gonna do it myself!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.0,
    "endTime": 185.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.0,
    "endTime": 185.0,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.0,
    "endTime": 185.0,
    "text": "You can't!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.0,
    "endTime": 188.0,
    "text": "You're only one IQ point away from being a vegetable!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.0,
    "endTime": 189.0,
    "text": "Question three!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.0,
    "endTime": 190.0,
    "text": "Question three!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.0,
    "endTime": 191.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.0,
    "endTime": 192.0,
    "text": "Here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.0,
    "endTime": 200.0,
    "text": "Okay, Waterson, I've marked your test, and I've got some bad news."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.0,
    "endTime": 203.0,
    "text": "I'll see you back in eighth grade tomorrow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.0,
    "endTime": 203.0,
    "text": "Look!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.0,
    "endTime": 207.0,
    "text": "You got an A-plus?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.0,
    "endTime": 208.0,
    "text": "But how?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 210.0,
    "text": "Must have been all the time we spent going over it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.0,
    "endTime": 212.0,
    "text": "Wait, so you actually..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.0,
    "endTime": 213.0,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.0,
    "endTime": 214.0,
    "text": "I actually learned something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.0,
    "endTime": 217.0,
    "text": "And a pleasure to keep you with us, too, Miss Simeon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.0,
    "endTime": 219.0,
    "text": "Good job, Waterson."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.0,
    "endTime": 222.0,
    "text": "I guess you didn't need me after all to help you cheat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.0,
    "endTime": 225.0,
    "text": "Use your pen for the test."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.0,
    "endTime": 227.0,
    "text": "Yeah, it really helped."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.0,
    "endTime": 230.0,
    "text": " It meant I could focus and didn't need to cheat like you did in the eighth grade."
  }
]